                         @{b}Future@{ub}

     Ok, some bugs affected the last version and this was specified in the
     manual. Now, after 11 months, i decided to remove them from the program
     and now @{b}ShapeGen@{ub} seems to be very stable.

     I think this program needs no more features. However, if someone
     has some idea about improving @{b}ShapeGen@{ub}, please try to
     @{" contact me " link SE_Author}.

@endnode

